cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with multi-target, multi-camera tracking systems and presents a new data set with annotated video frames. It could also belong to the machine learning (cs.MM) sub-category as it presents a reference software system as a comparison baseline. Additionally, it could be categorized under the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cryptography and security (cs.CR) as it deals with performance measures and error types. Finally, it could also be categorized under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) as it presents a new data set for training and testing multi-target, multi-camera tracking systems.
